# AGC conventions

- **Layout:** [README.md](README.md) — `agc-core` = `com.framework.agent.core` only (no Spring). `agc-spring-boot-starter` = main user dependency.
- **Tool path:** Governed calls only via **`ToolInvocationGateway`** (`agc-mcp`).
- **Pipeline:** Policy (`agc-policy`) then guardrails (`agc-guardrail`); **DENY** → no **`McpToolExecutor`**.
- **Audit:** `agc-audit` + `agc-storage`; append-only; no silent drops (metrics on failure).
- **Spec:** [docs/PRODUCT_DEVELOPMENT_PLAN.md](docs/PRODUCT_DEVELOPMENT_PLAN.md) · **layout:** [docs/ARCHITECTURE.md](docs/ARCHITECTURE.md)
